{
  "id": "adv_event_2401_01_01",
  "title": "沙季の大掃除",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dormitory-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dormitory-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――これは、NEXT VENUSグランプリで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――This happened during New Year’s‚ right after",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 2.8799999475,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "同時優勝を果たした直後の正月の出来事",
      "translations": {
        "en": "they won the NEXT VENUS Grand Prix.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.8799999475,
      "endTime": 5.0000000953,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣ちゃん、明けましておめでとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Happy New Year‚ Mei-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.2666667938,
      "endTime": 10.406666708,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "明けましておめでと～！　今年もよろしくね！\n……あれ？　沙季ちゃん一人だけ？　他のみんなは？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Happy New Year~! Let’s have another great year!\n…Oh? Are you alone‚ Saki-chan? Where’s everyone else?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.6000001271,
      "endTime": 22.184240849800002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "サニピの五人はお仕事に出かけました\n今日は夜まで帰れないそうです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The five Sunny Peace members went out for work.\nThey said they won’t be back until tonight.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.377574269,
      "endTime": 27.850386254,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんは実家でご家族とお正月を過ごしています\n今夜の年始ライブまでには戻ってくるそうです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono-chan is spending New Year’s with her family at her parents’ house.\nShe said she’ll be back before tonight’s New Year’s live performance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.0442409356,
      "endTime": 35.0442407449,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "そういえばすずにゃんも、元旦は\n親戚の集まりがあるから実家に帰るって言ってたっけ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come to think of it‚ Suzu-nyan also said\nshe was going back to her parents’ house for a family gathering on New Year’s Day.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.2442409356,
      "endTime": 42.7622003396,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "渚ちゃんも朝早くに出かけました\n友達の家に遊びに行くそうです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nagisa-chan also left early this morning.\nShe said she was going to a friend’s house.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.9555337588,
      "endTime": 48.337959829999996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "そっか……じゃあ、今日は沙季ちゃんと二人きりだね\nこたつに入ってお餅を食べながらゴロゴロしよう～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… So‚ it’s just the two of us today‚ Saki-chan.\nLet’s get in the kotatsu‚ eat some mochi‚ and be couch potatoes~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.5222004254,
      "endTime": 59.183039315500004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "ゴロゴロしません\nお正月だからって、そんな自堕落な生活は許しませんよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’re not going to be couch potatoes.\nI won’t allow such a lazy lifestyle‚ even if it’s New Year’s.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.3763727347,
      "endTime": 65.7363726775,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "という訳で、忙しくて年末に出来なかった大掃除を\n今から二人でやりましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ we’re going to do a big cleaning\nthat we couldn’t do at the end of the year because we were busy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.9430394013,
      "endTime": 72.08462646790001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "え～、芽衣はこたつでゴロゴロしたいな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ehh~‚ I want to be a couch potato in the kotatsu~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.2763727347,
      "endTime": 76.941316239,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "一年の計は元旦にあり！　身の回りを整理整頓して\n清々しい気持ちで新たな一年を始めましょう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The yearly plan is made on New Year’s Day! Let’s tidy up our surroundings\nand start the new year with a fresh mind!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.1346496581,
      "endTime": 85.1346494674,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "もの凄いやる気だね……\n……でも、そうだね。部屋が綺麗だと気持ちいいもんね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re so motivated…\n…But‚ you’re right. It feels good to have a clean room.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.3346496581,
      "endTime": 95.0752614974,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣も大掃除手伝うよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ll help you with the big cleaning!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.2685949165,
      "endTime": 97.68077181160001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます。では私は廊下をお掃除するので\n芽衣ちゃんはリビングをお願いします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you. Then I’ll clean the hallway‚\nso please take care of the living room‚ Mei-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.8741052308,
      "endTime": 105.0141053834,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "はーい！　頑張ってピカピカにしちゃうよ～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay! I’ll make it sparkle!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.2074385641,
      "endTime": 109.8513840673,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――小一時間後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――About an hour later.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.8447174864,
      "endTime": 112.0447174864,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01-ski009.m4a",
      "text": "ふぅ……やっと一段落付きました\n建物が広いとお掃除のしがいがありますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whew… I can finally catch my breath.\nIt's worth the effort to clean such a big building.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.9113872049,
      "endTime": 120.7357182978,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 16378.612795099996
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01-ski010.m4a",
      "text": "後は窓を全開にして、しばらく換気しておきましょう\nそう言えばリビングのお掃除はどうなったんでしょうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now let’s open all the windows and air out the place for a while.\nSpeaking of which‚ I wonder how the living room cleaning is going?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.9447205382,
      "endTime": 130.5748797256,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "あははは！　この漫画面白いな～\n続きはどこにあるんだろう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahahahaha! This manga is so funny~.\nI wonder where the next volume is?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.844719521,
      "endTime": 141.01354018819998,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8455.28047900001
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01-ski011.m4a",
      "text": "……芽衣ちゃん。どうしてこたつに入って\n漫画を読んでいるんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Mei-chan. Why are you in the kotatsu\nreading Manga?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.1068675039,
      "endTime": 147.1272983549,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_02-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "沙季ちゃん！\nこの漫画の続き、どこにあるか知らない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Saki-chan!\nDo you know where the next volume of this Manga is?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.3402008372,
      "endTime": 151.6982281047,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01-ski012.m4a",
      "text": "知りません\nサボってないで、ちゃんとお掃除して下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don’t know.\nStop slacking off and clean properly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.8915615239,
      "endTime": 156.4486134686,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01-mei010.m4a",
      "text": "あ……そう言えばお掃除の途中だっけ\nごめんごめん。面白そうな漫画を見つけて、つい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh… right‚ we were in the middle of cleaning.\nSorry‚ sorry. I found an interesting Manga and got carried away…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.6582281905,
      "endTime": 166.34233215630002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01-mei011.m4a",
      "text": "すぐ片付けるから。えっと、この漫画は……\nその辺の棚に適当に入れておけばいいよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ll put this away right now. Let’s see‚ this Manga…\nI’ll just randomly put it on that shelf over there",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 166.4689968743,
      "endTime": 176.5298363366,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01-ski013.m4a",
      "text": "「適当に」……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“Randomly”… ?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 176.7231697557,
      "endTime": 178.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01-mei012.m4a",
      "text": "……あれ？\nこんな所にDVDが置きっぱなしになってる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Oh?\nThere’s a DVD left here.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 178.8231768765,
      "endTime": 183.5328820384,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01-mei013.m4a",
